headline: Accenture Acquires MomentumABM, Expanding Marketing Advisory and Account-Based Marketing Capabilities for B2B Growth
summary: LONDON, September 04, 2025--Accenture has acquired MomentumABM, a growth consultancy headquartered in the UK, recognized for advancing account-based marketing (ABM) strategies.

headline: How Accenture’s CEO Took the Leap From Law to Consulting
summary: Accenture CEO Julie Sweet leads one of the world’s largest workforces—and is navigating an era defined by AI disruption, geopolitical volatility, and shifting global markets. In this segment of the Fortune 500: Titans and Disruptors of Industry vodcast, she shares how she advises fellow CEOs to reinvent their companies, reflects on her unconventional leap from law to CEO, and opens up about the lessons that shaped her rise to one of the most powerful roles in business.
